{"tid":494450,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無類風濕關節炎巴絲入黎傾下計","createTime":"2017-12-09T15:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T09:12:49.000Z","uid":74823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8780f8bdef0a8ead077015a2c34ff87b71d15d3","tid":494450,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"我今年19歲 應該係上年9月中發病 <br />\n但拖左一年先知有類風濕 應該都算遲左少少<br />\n<br />\n每日起身都有1-2隻手指腫 一時會頸痛 腳爭痛 膝頭哥痛 <br />\n其實好驚手指變形<br />\n<br />\n我就岩岩食左一個月中藥 情況反反覆覆咁<br />\n希望快啲減藥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天氣凍 記得保暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家講下自己病左幾耐 情況？"},{"pid":"7dcc73b86a4694740e2ac2417f816ff1a4721930","tid":494450,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"b51c8f4e447834a3b801db7e0c07ae2f8e3783f3","tid":494450,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95195a59d9380daa13718e0b7f0d003ed3b12569","tid":494450,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:46:56.000Z","msg":"無人既"},{"pid":"4b38162553f06f43649abfa81055163b1967f5e7","tid":494450,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd529450dd67b4d6ac114a250e0205313626a81","tid":494450,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"無人呀"},{"pid":"07eecc15f2b1879c5a674d8d7d698610a0379c64","tid":494450,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"病左五六年都有<br />\n一開始睇過針灸跌打幾個月<br />\n唔同診所醫生都睇過幾次都無咩用<br />\n<br />\n最後放棄keep住睇政府風濕科幾個月覆診一次抽血拎藥睇報告穩定住<br />\n一種長期藥 一種有痛先食既消炎止痛藥連胃藥<br />\n後者連續食得多幾傷胃 個肚會keep住痛<br />\n但我類風濕痛既位置係兩邊大臂外側 有時條腰都有事<br />\n唔keep住食藥的話行路極辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唉</span>"}]}